я╗┐{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":112161,"duration_api_ms":107748,"num_turns":18,"result":"# Functions for Building / Rebuilding the Code Graph\n\nSources searched via tree-sitter MCP: `mcp__tree-sitter__list_files`, `find_text`, and `get_symbols` against the registered `source` project (236 Rust files).\n\n## Top-level CLI entry points\n\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:149` ├втВмтАЭ `pub async fn run(...)` ├втВмтАЭ main `mneme build` entry; orchestrates the full graph-build pipeline (intent ├втАатАЩ git ├втАатАЩ extract ├втАатАЩ embeddings ├втАатАЩ leiden ├втАатАЩ architecture ├втАатАЩ conventions ├втАатАЩ wiki ├втАатАЩ perf ├втАатАЩ errors ├втАатАЩ agents ├втАатАЩ federated ├втАатАЩ livestate).\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:259` ├втВмтАЭ `pub async fn run_dispatched(...)` ├втВмтАЭ variant that dispatches selected passes only.\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:393` ├втВмтАЭ `async fn run_inline(...)` ├втВмтАЭ runs the build pipeline without spawning a daemon.\n- `cli/src/commands/rebuild.rs:67` ├втВмтАЭ `pub async fn run(...)` ├втВмтАЭ `mneme rebuild` entry; discards cached graph for a project and re-parses from scratch (tries IPC `Rebuild`, falls back to direct DB).\n- `cli/src/commands/rebuild.rs:211` ├втВмтАЭ `fn count_graph(...)` ├втВмтАЭ reads `(nodes, edges)` totals from the graph DB so rebuild can report what was discarded.\n- `cli/src/commands/graphify.rs:46` ├втВмтАЭ `pub async fn run(...)` ├втВмтАЭ `mneme graphify` entry; runs the in-process Rust extractors against the project (or forwards via supervisor).\n\n## Per-pass graph-builders inside `build.rs`\n\n(Each writes a different subset of nodes/edges into the graph shard.)\n\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:1395` ├втВмтАЭ `run_multimodal_pass` ├втВмтАЭ extracts multimodal/asset nodes.\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:1647` ├втВмтАЭ `run_leiden_pass` ├втВмтАЭ runs Leiden community detection over the built graph.\n- `cli/src/commands/build.rs:1925` ├втВмтАЭ