тАЭ `fn reindex(communities)` ├втВмтАЭ stable re-numbering of community IDs after the graph is clustered.\n\n## Risk / architecture-derived sub-indexes\n\n- `scanners/src/scanners/architecture.rs:225` ├втВмтАЭ `fn build_risk_index(nodes)` ├втВмтАЭ builds the per-community risk index consumed by `run_architecture_pass`.\n\n## Benchmark harness builders\n\n- `benchmarks/src/lib.rs:173` ├втВмтАЭ `pub async fn index_repo(project)` ├втВмтАЭ runs a full build/index against a repo and returns an `IndexReport` (used by perf benchmarks).\n- `benchmarks/src/lib.rs:606` ├втВмтАЭ `pub fn shard_graph_db(project)` ├втВмтАЭ returns/creates the graph-DB shard path for benchmark runs.\n- `benchmarks/src/bin/bench_retrieval.rs:172` ├втВмтАЭ `async fn cmd_index(repo)` ├втВмтАЭ bench CLI wrapper around `index_repo`.\n\n---\n\nNote: I deliberately excluded `supervisor/src/api_graph.rs` `api_graph_*` handlers (e.g. `api_graph_nodes`, `api_graph_edges`, `api_graph_file_tree`, ├втВм┬ж) ├втВмтАЭ those *read* the already-built graph for the UI; they don't construct or rebuild it.\n\nFiles cited (all opened via `mcp__tree-sitter__find_text` / `get_symbols`):\n`cli/src/commands/build.rs`, `cli/src/commands/rebuild.rs`, `cli/src/commands/graphify.rs`, `cli/src/commands/blast.rs`, `cli/src/commands/godnodes.rs`, `cli/src/commands/recall.rs`, `cli/src/commands/shard_summary.rs`, `supervisor/src/watcher.rs`, `supervisor/src/ipc.rs`, `store/src/builder.rs`, `parsers/src/extractor.rs`, `parsers/src/incremental.rs`, `brain/src/cluster_runner.rs`, `scanners/src/scanners/architecture.rs`, `benchmarks/src/lib.rs`, `benchmarks/src/bin/bench_retrieval.rs`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"e1bc557a-dd43-4301-81f8-3bb19acab69b","total_cost_usd":1.2095655,"usage":{"input_tokens":19,"cache_creation_input_tokens":116898,"cache_read_input_tokens":564966,"output_tokens":7855,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_t